today.
   The fire aboard the Golden Alaska was reported just before 11:30
p.m. Tuesday.
   Rosie Davis, nursing supervisor at Harborview Medical Center,
said that four people were treated for minor injuries.
   Coast Guard Petty Officer Frank Klucznik said fire crews had to
