<HEAD>Government Preparing to Free Nearly 1,000 Political Prisoners</HEAD>
<DATELINE>MEXICO CITY (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The government, which has announced plans to
release more than 400 political prisoners, is preparing to free
